      ﾛ ﾛ On with the update release information:                        ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ NOTE: This is a cumulative update - you can install it on any  ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ game version.                                                  ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ ------------------------                                       ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ Update v1.18 Changelist                                        ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ ------------------------                                       ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fix bug where purchasing capital ship levels would give you  ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ a refund.                                                      ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * AntiMedium DamageType's modifier vs. Medium armor reduced    ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ from 150% to 133%                                              ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Numerous balanche changes for all Factions.                  ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * New skybox!!! Blair's favorite one!!! (Actually, it isn't    ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ new but up until this point it was only used in screenshots.   ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ There was a bug in the data referencing which meant it was     ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ never selected in-game until now!)                             ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Sound fixes: AnimaTempest, EMPBlast, ReactiveNaniteArmor,    ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ NanoHullRepair                                                 ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Amended descriptions for research labs.                      ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Show error message with info when textures don't match up to ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ make it easier for modders to track down the offending         ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ textures and what is wrong with them.                          ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * New BonusMaxSquads buff modifier type.                       ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Optimized various situations that could occur late game and  ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ slow the game down unneccessarily.                             ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fix crash if autorecord.cache is somehow set to read-only.   ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fixed corrupt save game bug.                                 ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fixed potential graphics crash. Updated shaders so they're   ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ not broken by the March 2009 DirectX.                          ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fixed various rare crash                                     ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ fixes.                                                         ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ ------------------------                                       ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ Update v1.17 Changelist                                        ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ ------------------------                                       ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * All race's carrier cruiser's max speed reduced from 500 to   ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ 450.                                                           ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fixed a bug in the pathfinder that caused it to favor        ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ sub-optimal paths for between system travel.                   ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fixed incorrect start conditions on Double Cross map.        ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Tweaked the equation for damage reduction so that it is more ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ stable for large negative armor values.                        ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Magnetic Cloud orbit bodies now disable all abilities, not   ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ just those requiring antimatter.                               ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Missile Barrage missile travel effect made unique from its   ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ normal missile weapon's effect.                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fixed the potential for extra gaps in the text of            ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ multiplayer chat.                                              ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fixed missing multiplayer chat characters with some          ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ non-English languages.                                         ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fixed not being able to create ICO account and player names  ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ with certain non-English characters.                           ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fixed a bug that could cause the ICO lobby to disappear.     ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Income summaries no longer overflow in such a way that per   ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ planet elements are mis-rendered.                              ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fixed some bad zooming behavior when you try and get too     ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ close (especially on small entities like fighters).            ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fixed a bug where you couldn't zoom in past a certain        ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ distance despite changes to the zoom scalar for the given      ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ entity. The minimum distance is still restricted to the        ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ entity's radius or 20m for objects will spatial extents (e.g.  ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ debris).                                                       ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fixed zoom scaling bug (see above).                          ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fixed a rare crash bug caused by Jump Degradation ability of ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ Overseer cruisers.                                             ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Fixed a rare sync error caused by loading differences        ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ between FAT32 and NTFS file                                    ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ systems.                                                       ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ ------------------------                                       ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ Update v1.16 Changelist                                        ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ ------------------------                                       ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * GalaxyForge maps now have their own directory and are no     ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ longer reliant on the manifest system. Once created, these     ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ should be placed in the appropriate directory (e.g on XP       ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ C:\Documents and Settings\username\Local Settings\Application  ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ Data\Ironclad Games\Sins of a Solar Empire\GalaxyForge).       ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Recorded game playback no longer causes auto-saved game      ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ files to be generated.                                         ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ * Massive memory savings paricularly for large games.          ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ WARNING: This update will invalidate existing save games.      ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
